<p>\subsection{Chern Number}
We call the following quantity the Chern number:
\(\begin{equation}
C_n = \frac{1}{2\pi}\int_S \mathbf{F}_n \cdot d\mathbf{S} = n\in \ZZ
\end{equation}\)</p>

